From c17564da59b83a9ef6f2ab56c86ee6c2142bf05f Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Acorn Build <build@acorn>
Date: Thu, 23 Apr 2026 18:18:42 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] feat: auth, roles, dark/light mode, task drawer, marketing
 tab, AI budget, audit trail

- AuthContext: org-gated sign-in (acornactivations.co.za), admin/manager/viewer roles
- ThemeContext: dark/light toggle with localStorage persistence
- SignInPage: domain-restricted login screen
- TaskDetailDrawer: comments, document uploads, manager sign-off per task
- TasksTab: clickable rows opening detail drawer
- MarketingTab: Howler ticket tracking + flyer distribution per channel
- AIBudgetTab: Claude-powered budget advisor with follow-up chat
- AuditTrailTab: filterable activity log
- AppShell: theme toggle + user role badge + sign-out menu
- AppSidebar: admin-only nav section
- styles.css: full light mode token set
- SQL schema: task_comments, task_documents, task_signoffs, audit_log, marketing, flyers
